{"tid":1010444,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"做乜一到新年個個親戚都咁鍾意做就業輔導員？？","createTime":"2019-02-06T04:05:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T04:51:25.000Z","uid":23170,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7acd5b605379bed8c786a7d0e17e2cc910898c7b","tid":1010444,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:05:21.000Z","msg":"一到新年發覺個個親戚最鍾意就係講邊個個仔邊個個女做緊啲乜，又俾晒建議。<br />\n<br />\n做乜一到新年就咁鍾意討論依啲嘢，又會俾晒意見話邊份工好呀，依家做緊嗰份唔夠好呀。好似望過晒CV俾晒專業建議咁。仲要發覺係範範都會講，由大公司去到政府工又有唔同專業資格，應該讀返書又點點點。其實香港係咪真係剩返返工係值得搬上枱面講<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申，廢青<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c6552fe967fc2a5aa17c0dadc32408794bad67","tid":1010444,"uid":24160,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:06:33.000Z","msg":"講完返工<br />\n就變身做婚姻介紹員<br />\n問你幾時拍拖<br />\n<br />\n聽到都<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89147e72b96056e7ab18d8333345b357588888ce","tid":1010444,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:07:00.000Z","msg":"乖乖地聽長輩教導<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 塞錢落你袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cadd233f4b89b3eade225cfee1e769189330a43","tid":1010444,"uid":23170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"89147e72b96056e7ab18d8333345b357588888ce","tid":1010444,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:07:00.000Z","msg":"乖乖地聽長輩教導<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 塞錢落你袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T04:07:48.000Z","msg":"塞真錢我會開心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47bcd678703b9f2bebd5f9142a66ffbe2c38c8a0","tid":1